2011-xx-xx  Keith Nash  <kjnash@users.sourceforge.net>

	* Update to correspond to tk8.x/text.tcl 1.41.4.3 (tagged Tk 8.5.9),
	  1.46.
	* Don't call private commands from tk8.x/text.tcl (for improved
	  compatibility with all versions of Tk 8.5.x, 8.6.x).
	* Adapt bindings to have Mac-like behaviour on the Mac.
	* Show correct cursor for insert/overwrite when there are multiple
	  widgets.
	* Fix "Smart End" to handle trailing whitespace.
	* Different behaviour for "Smart Home" in corner case with wrapped
	  leading whitespace.
	* Update docs and examples.

